      • setAccess

        public void setAccess(Conference the_con,
             AccessLevel the_level)
        Assigns the user an access level for a given conference. If the conference is not in the user's conference list, it is added.
        Parameters:
        the_con - Conference to assign privileges to.
        the_level - The access level to this conference that the user will gain.

      • removeAccess

        public void removeAccess(Conference the_con,
                AccessLevel the_level)
        Removes one given level of access from the user for a given conference. If the user only has one responsibility, the entire conference is removed from their list.
        Parameters:
        the_con - The conference to edit.
        the_level - The access level to be removed.
